{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Black_Butterfly_vs_Slush",
  "title": "35 ISY Competition: Black Butterfly vs. Slush",
  "summary": "In a simulator dueling competition during the 35 ISY games, the pilot Liza (flying as \"Slush\") faces Sarai (flying as \"Black Butterfly\") in a one-on-one starfighter match. The two trade volleys across many rounds, the cockpit voice calling out dropping shield levels as each pilot mixes gunnery and evasive flying. Liza pilots aggressively and lands repeated telling hits, while Sarai struggles to connect her shots despite some excellent piloting rolls. Momentary lapses and sloppy passes keep the contest tense, but Liza's steadier gunnery gradually wears Black Butterfly down. The match plays out as a back-and-forth of skill checks and maneuvering, with Slush holding the upper hand through the engagement.",
